### 1. Create a new Miles Reward (POST)
# Expected: 201 Created
# Response body should be the created miles reward object with a generated ID.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/miles-rewards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": 1,
  "flightId": 1,
  "date": "2025-12-21"
}

### 2. Get All Miles Rewards (GET)
# Expected: 200 OK
# Response body should be a JSON array of all miles rewards.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/miles-rewards

### 3. Get Miles Reward by ID (GET)
# Expected: 200 OK
# Response body should be the miles reward with ID 1.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/miles-rewards/1

### 4. Update Miles Reward (PUT)
# Expected: 200 OK
# Response body should be the updated miles reward object.
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/miles-rewards/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": 1,
  "flightId": 1,
  "date": "2025-12-22"
}

### 5. Verify Update (GET)
# Expected: 200 OK
# Response body should be the miles reward with the updated date "2025-12-22".
GET http://localhost:8080/api/miles-rewards/1

### 6. Delete Miles Reward (DELETE)
# Expected: 204 No Content
# No response body.
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/miles-rewards/1

### 7. Verify Deletion (GET)
# Expected: 404 Not Found
# Error response body.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/miles-rewards/1